ctiveness of our model design and benefits of\nthe new MBHT framework. Our implementation code is released at:\nhttps://github.com/yuh-yang/MBHT-KDD22.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 15:07:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 06:42:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
