MA interferometric data processed using\nCASA, but the principles are generally applicable to most similar cm to sub-mm\nimaging.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 15:12:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
